components.templateData:
<hr
  data-testid="hr"
  [class]="'ion-divider-' + orientation + ' ion-divider-' + type"
  [attr.data-content]="
    orientation === 'horizontal' ? (type === 'text' ? label : '') : ''
  "
/>

components.name: IonIconComponent
components.templateData:
<svg
  attr.height.px="{{ size }}"
  attr.width.px="{{ size }}"
  attr.fill="{{ color }}"
  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
  [id]="'ion-icon-' + type"
  #svg
></svg>
